payload/webos25-truehd/  --  webOS-25 (C5-class) TrueHD/MLP decoder payload
===========================================================================

Profile: webos25-armel-gst124   (VERIFIED mechanism -- see ../../README.md)

This is the TrueHD/MLP half of the unified webOS-25 mechanism (the DTS half is
in ../webos25/). Drop these cross-built ARM soft-float (armel, EABI5) binaries
HERE before packaging the .ipk:

    libgstlibav.so              gst-libav 1.18 with avdec_truehd / avdec_mlp
    libavcodec.so.*  (+soname symlinks)   minimal ffmpeg n4.4.4 (truehd+mlp only)
    libavutil.so.*   (+soname symlinks)
    libavformat.so.* (+soname symlinks)
    libavfilter.so.* (+soname symlinks)
    libswresample.so.*(+soname symlinks)

Keep the version symlinks (libavcodec.so.58 -> libavcodec.so.58.x.y): the load
chain libgstlibav -> libavcodec -> libavutil resolves by soname, and every real
.so carries RPATH /var/lib/webosbrew/truehd/libs.

Where they come from
--------------------
    cd ../../../webos25
    ./build-truehd.sh          # -> webos25/truehd-out/libgstlibav.so + libav*/libsw*
    cp -P truehd-out/libgstlibav.so truehd-out/libav*.so* truehd-out/libsw*.so* \
       ../dts-enabler-universal/payload/webos25-truehd/

At enable time the JS service copies these to:
    /var/lib/webosbrew/truehd/libgstlibav.so
    /var/lib/webosbrew/truehd/libs/libav*.so* , libsw*.so*
then bind-mounts our libgstlibav over LG's TrueHD-less
/usr/lib/gstreamer-1.0/libgstlibav.so, adds TRUEHD/MLP to the umediaserver codec
capability config and avdec_truehd/mlp=310 to gstcool.conf [sw_decoder] (both by
editing the TV's own live /etc files -- no LG config is shipped), and regenerates
the media GStreamer registry with LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/var/lib/webosbrew/truehd/libs.

ABI constraints (must hold or the plugin will not load on the C5)
-----------------------------------------------------------------
  - 32-bit ARM, EABI5 soft-float  (loader ld-linux.so.3, e_flags 0x05000200)
  - max referenced GLIBC symbol <= GLIBC_2.35  (TV has glibc 2.35)
  - gst-libav 1.18 plugin ABI (loads in the TV's 1.24 -- verified on-device)

These .so files are NOT committed (see ../../.gitignore). ffmpeg/gst-libav are
LGPL-2.1+; ship the corresponding source offer with any distributed .ipk.
